{"tid":19614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普親自推文 稱呼蔡英文為「台灣總統」","createTime":"2016-12-03T01:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T11:23:01.000Z","uid":35790,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50b508abe3a2336f568464bd945e3dc9953386e7","tid":19614,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"川普親自推文 稱呼蔡英文「台灣總統」<br />\n<br />\n2016/12/03 08:56&nbsp;48018<br />\n<br />\n美國總統當選人川普今日早晨8時50分左右，親自在推特上推文說：「台灣總統今天打電話給我，祝賀我當選總統。謝謝你！」<br />\n<br />\n其實稍早外國媒體就紛紛報導，川普已經和蔡英文通過電話，川普交接團隊也證實，雙方就政治、經濟與安全問題進行討論。總統府隨後也公布兩人的10多分鐘談話內容，包括蔡英文祝賀川普順利當選美國新任總統，並對亞洲區域情勢交換意見等。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161203/640_846af7cbb2f20a0a3aa31a7877b1cb3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161203%2F640_846af7cbb2f20a0a3aa31a7877b1cb3d.jpg&h=17250402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161203/1003483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20161203%2F1003483&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lewT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=dd77d614\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161203/1003483</a>"},{"pid":"0e88d262523392ac860390e434b0bc3cb06a042a","tid":19614,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:47:16.000Z","msg":"玻璃心碎"},{"pid":"fcd495f43e5fef6327a9dd7eac3c929064d69770","tid":19614,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"Trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n41J <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a59b5bf71dc22bddc70bd648c8d16e2b0e7bf10","tid":19614,"uid":1697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85b907340d820ccd81d3041b959a45023cfbb9b","tid":19614,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:49:13.000Z","msg":"IN TRUMP WR TRUST"},{"pid":"2e7483341b32cc9698900914161fdabc5a8ade3a","tid":19614,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:50:44.000Z","msg":"入慘，我信<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cdd1c00605d533084c6ae495cc7864fc8a61ba","tid":19614,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:50:54.000Z","msg":"川普與小英通話　白宮重申「一個中國」<br />\n<br />\n2016/12/03 07:59&nbsp;3103<br />\n<br />\n美國總統當選人川普在昨日與總統蔡英文通電話，美國白宮得知消息後，重申「一個中國」原則，承認北京政府是一中的唯一政權。<br />\n<br />\n《法新社》報導指出，川普與小英通話一事，可視為打破美國長年來的慣例。但美國國家安全發言人荷恩(Emily Horne)說：「我們對海峽兩岸的政策，長期以來並沒有改變。我們基於《美中三個聯合公報與台灣關係法》，堅定承認『一中』政策，維持海峽兩岸的和平與穩定，是我方根本利益。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161203/1003463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20161203%2F1003463&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lewT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=676b72f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161203/1003463</a><br />\n<br />\n無違反一國中國原則"},{"pid":"72d464c8498b3871c683aa1303161809c8b41b26","tid":19614,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>川普與小英通話　白宮重申「一個中國」<br />\n<br />\n2016/12/03 07:59&amp;nbsp;3103<br />\n<br />\n美國總統當選人川普在昨日與總統蔡英文通電話，美國白宮得知消息後，重申「一個中國」原則，承認北京政府是一中的唯一政權。<br />\n<br />\n《法新社》報導指出，川普與小英通話一事，可視為打破美國長年來的慣例。但美國國家安全發言人荷恩(Emily Horne)說：「我們對海峽兩岸的政策，長期以來並沒有改變。我們基於《美中三個聯合公報與台灣關係法》，堅定承認『一中』政策，維持海峽兩岸的和平與穩定，是我方根本利益。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161203/1003463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20161203%2F1003463&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lewT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=676b72f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161203/1003463</a><br />\n<br />\n無違反一國中國原則</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白宮仲係奧巴馬話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ntrump 上左當就好難講"},{"pid":"218d01ba11dca424a998cf2dd293100796b651dc","tid":19614,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd97aa7c1f0044c8f70b55762a70384e45b775da","tid":19614,"uid":6639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"人地宜家叫台灣 咁咪得返一個中國囉"},{"pid":"0945ca12ba3d430b5fde788fb8ee63c971e08ccf","tid":19614,"uid":4340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"President of Taiwan<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70308e3eae6f968bfd973c501e05372f5d1a2b1","tid":19614,"uid":38797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地宜家叫台灣 咁咪得返一個中國囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n盲腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfa0ea5a6cedeed32c4315136e924098fd91068","tid":19614,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"